  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the allure of older idols in this drama game about an older group making a comeback from retirement, featuring a GxB/BxB/non-binary romance! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆ Choose your love interest:  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💙 Frey (He/Him)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>VA: Patrick Langner</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911260/extras/444aa669df873c6905496d0a080288bb.avif?t=1771709662\" alt=\"Frey Character Profile\" width=600 height=382 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❤️ Hawkins (He/Him)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>VA: Conlin Rei</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911260/extras/4809b12ab783061c1f26d9cff0949d72.avif?t=1771709662\" alt=\"Hawkins Character Profile\" width=600 height=382 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💚 Mikael (They/Them)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>VA: Jonathon Dull</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911260/extras/c9a6084ae3f54b3ecfc5c3a54b8d916f.avif?t=1771709662\" alt=\"Mikael Character Profile\" width=600 height=382 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>■ Game Experience</u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Stellifier” is a choice-driven, visual novel where you play as a journalist, covering the scoop of the year - the comeback of Stellifier, a group of older idols attempting to re-debut. Will you write about their journey or will you fall for their charm amongst the three idol love interests (male or non-binary).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>■ Features</u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Play as a female, male, or non-binary MC </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Unlockable CGs through a snapchat-like feature and an instagram-like feature</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Voiced in-game messages</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > -Unlockable Achievements</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the allure of older idols in this drama game about an older group making a comeback from retirement, featuring a GxB/BxB/non-binary romance! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆ Choose your love interest:  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💙 Frey (He/Him)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>VA: Patrick Langner</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911260/extras/444aa669df873c6905496d0a080288bb.avif?t=1771709662\" alt=\"Frey Character Profile\" width=600 height=382 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❤️ Hawkins (He/Him)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>VA: Conlin Rei</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911260/extras/4809b12ab783061c1f26d9cff0949d72.avif?t=1771709662\" alt=\"Hawkins Character Profile\" width=600 height=382 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💚 Mikael (They/Them)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>VA: Jonathon Dull</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2911260/extras/c9a6084ae3f54b3ecfc5c3a54b8d916f.avif?t=1771709662\" alt=\"Mikael Character Profile\" width=600 height=382 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>■ Game Experience</u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Stellifier” is a choice-driven, visual novel where you play as a journalist, covering the scoop of the year - the comeback of Stellifier, a group of older idols attempting to re-debut. Will you write about their journey or will you fall for their charm amongst the three idol love interests (male or non-binary).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>■ Features</u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Play as a female, male, or non-binary MC </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Unlockable CGs through a snapchat-like feature and an instagram-like feature</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Voiced in-game messages</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > -Unlockable Achievements</p>",
